fields.title: ORDER STATUS
fields.notification_title: Your order has been updated to $status
fields.notification_body: Your order has been updated to $status

fields.title: PICKUP_ORDER_PLACED_SMS
fields.notification_body:
Hi {customer},

Your order has been received! Your food will be ready for pick-up at {estimated_time} at {restaurant_name}. If you have any questions about your order, feel free to call us at {restaurant_phone}. 

Thank you for choosing {restaurant_name}! See you soon.

fields.title: PICKUP_ORDER_ACCEPTED_SMS
fields.notification_body:
Your food is ready for pick-up! You can collect it at {restaurant_name} located at {restaurant_address}. 

Thank you for ordering from us. Enjoy your meal!

fields.title: DELIVERY_ORDER_PLACED_SMS
fields.notification_body:
Hi {customer},

Your order has been received! If you have any questions about your order, feel free to call us at {restaurant_phone}. 

Thank you for choosing {restaurant_name}! See you soon.

fields.title: DELIVERY_ORDER_ACCEPTED_SMS
fields.notification_body:
Hi {customer},

Your order has been accepted! Your food will be ready for delivery at {estimated_time}. Your dasher's number is {dasher_number}. If you have any delivery-related queries, please contact the dasher. For any issues with your order, call us at {restaurant_phone}.
Click this link to track your order on the map: {tracking_link}.

Thank you for choosing {restaurant_name}! Enjoy your meal.

fields.title: ORDER_CANCEL_SMS
fields.notification_body:
Dear {customer},
We regret to inform you that your order #{order_id} has been canceled due to unforeseen circumstances. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.
For any queries or assistance, please feel free to contact us at {restaurant_phone}. We appreciate your understanding.
Thank you,
{restaurant_name}
